children.text: # Determine mapping of record keys to syslog keys

SYSLOG_HEADERS.each do |key_name|
        conf_key = "#{key_name}_key"
        @mappings[key_name] = conf[conf_key] if conf.key?(conf_key)
      end

do |key_name|

        @mappings[key_name] = conf[conf_key] if conf.key?(conf_key)
      end
